### advertiser 목록 조회
GET {{host}}/advertisers

### advertiser 단건 조회
GET {{host}}/advertisers/1

### advertiser 생성
POST {{host}}/advertisers
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"name": "테스트 광고주"
}

### advertiser 수정
PATCH {{host}}/advertisers/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"name": "수정된 광고주"
}

### advertiser 삭제
DELETE {{host}}/advertisers/1
